    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E92 M3, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 with its signature 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This specimen is mechanically flawless, having undergone preventative rod bearing replacement using VAC coated shells and ARP bolts to ensure long-term reciprocating assembly integrity. The 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile, short-throw engagement, paired with a perfectly calibrated variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damping Control (EDC), maintaining factory-spec damping rates and zero bushing deflection. Finished in Alpine White over pristine Novillo leather, this vehicle displays no bolster wear or exterior imperfections, representing a turn-key investment for the discerning collector.",
