      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing, providing an uncompromising 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential. Mechanically, this vehicle is superlative: the critical rod bearing service and VANOS overhaul have been performed proactively. The chassis exhibits zero subframe fatigue, and the suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications. Finished in Carbon Black Metallic, the exterior retains its deep luster with no paint imperfections, while the interior features supple, wear-free Nappa leather. A technically flawless example for the purist collector.",
